/>
</picture></div></div><div
class="block-intro-text"><p>A corporation is a legal entity completely separate from its owners, thereby limiting their liability. Corporations also issue shares of stock that are easily transferable. Incorporating is a good option for businesses wanting to attract investors.</p></div></div></div></div><div
class="section-content"><div
class="container"><div
class="narrow-container"><div
class="block block-how-to"><h2 id=how-to-incorporate>How to Incorporate:</h2><div
class="how-to-info"><div
class="info">
